        <mxCell id="AA5P-qOjUl-CRV39_Xl2-1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=21;" value="Component : it is going to manage the UI.==&amp;gt; it will maange a button , text box or form or 10 tables anything.&lt;div&gt;it is a building block of UI.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
